==English==

===Etymology===
From {{Ja.}} {{term|財テク|tr=zaiteku|sc=Jpan||money management}} < blend of {{term|財務|tr=zaimu|sc=Jpan||financial dealings}} and {{term|テクノロジー|tr=tekunorojii|sc=Jpan||technology}}, the latter < [[English]] {{term|technology}}. The ''-tech'' in ''zaitech'' reflects the original borrowing of English ''technology''.

